    "name": "UNCRACKED",
    "steam_appid": 3114420,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114420/extras/274c98cb0ec78e63989a000d7b2dac91.poster.avif?t=1770644630\" width=800 height=165 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114420/extras/274c98cb0ec78e63989a000d7b2dac91.webm?t=1770644630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在电池式笼养农场的黑暗角落里，远离人类收集者的视线，两支觉醒鸡蛋的敌对派系之间正爆发着无尽的战争。对它们来说，人类是无法战胜的威胁，没有任何武器能对抗，只有欺骗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >它们共同的目标是活过残酷的人类收蛋行动，而这迫使它们为未觉醒的鸡蛋展开残暴的争夺。这些鸡蛋是它们唯一的机会——作为替代蛋壳，为它们带来多活几天的希望……至少撑到下一次收集。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114420/extras/e3e09114c2793479eb13447948da6c1f.webp?t=1770644630\" width=136 height=56 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >酥脆动作与蛋黄血浆 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 破裂的蛋壳、飞溅的蛋黄，以及随着关卡推进愈发残酷的混乱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114420/extras/fe070ec77339e12276d8f1bd07f82716.poster.avif?t=1770644630\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114420/extras/fe070ec77339e12276d8f1bd07f82716.webm?t=1770644630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114420/extras/fe070ec77339e12276d8f1bd07f82716.mp4?t=1770644630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >按你的节奏游玩 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 小心翼翼地从掩体移动到掩体，或直接跳入战场，粉碎一切能动的东西。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >武器库与即兴战斗 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 手枪、霰弹枪、狙击步枪、机枪……或者干脆踢、跳、扔你手上能找到的东西。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114420/extras/38e69f5d31db755a558a80e1d7e8f644.poster.avif?t=1770644630\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114420/extras/38e69f5d31db755a558a80e1d7e8f644.webm?t=1770644630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114420/extras/38e69f5d31db755a558a80e1d7e8f644.mp4?t=1770644630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >笼养战场 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 探索电池笼农场的每个角落，对抗充满嗜“黄”敌人的多样环境。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >幽默的故事？真的</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 体验一个发生在非凡世界中的非凡故事：一个普通鸡蛋拒绝被打破……或被采集。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114420/extras/ad297eee3e0495db6fd4b4eb776199ef.poster.avif?t=1770644630\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114420/extras/ad297eee3e0495db6fd4b4eb776199ef.webm?t=1770644630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114420/extras/ad297eee3e0495db6fd4b4eb776199ef.mp4?t=1770644630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><u>帮助 UNCRACKED 说出你的语言</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>部分翻译仍较为粗略，并会随着时间不断改进。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>如果你是母语使用者并愿意帮助润色翻译，欢迎与我联系。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>所有贡献者都将被署名，并获得额外奖励。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114420/extras/073c5c65617f243720df99310432e778.avif?t=1770644630\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114420/extras_big/073c5c65617f243720df99310432e778.avif?t=1770644630 width=800 height=157 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Marty's Makings 是一个由一人组成的工作室。Martin 是一名没有任何经验的自学开发者，利用业余时间打造自己的首款游戏。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114420/extras/a9129ae9d06f16c6a91aacf48221ba35.poster.avif?t=1770644630\" width=600 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114420/extras/a9129ae9d06f16c6a91aacf48221ba35.webm?t=1770644630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114420/extras/a9129ae9d06f16c6a91aacf48221ba35.mp4?t=1770644630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
